            <a href="/services" class="text-white/80 hover:text-white">Services</a> > 
            <span class="text-white font-medium">Invoice Financing</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="heading-primary text-white mb-6">AI-Driven Invoice Financing: Accelerate Your Cash Flow Today</h1>
          <p class="hero-subtitle max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            Unlock 80-100% of your invoice value immediately with smart invoice financing for commercial trades and civil contractors. No more waiting 30-90 days for payment - get paid now and keep projects flowing.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center button-gap mb-8">
            <a href="/get-quote?service=invoice-financing" class="btn-primary btn-large">Get Instant Quote</a>
            <a href="/invoice-calculator" class="btn-secondary btn-large bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-secondary-dark">Invoice Calculator</a>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-white/90">
            <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
